inois]]\n[[Category:2020 in Illinois|coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:Disasters in Illinois]]\n[[Category:Health in Illinois]]\n[[Category:March 2020 events in the United States|coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:April 2020 events in the United States|coronavirus pandemic]]\n", "name_user": "Mr Xaero", "label": "safe", "comment": "date change", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Illinois"}
